  "payload": {
    "compiled_summary": "CoinHSL Family: solves Canonical family lineage for staged CoinHSL sparse-direct backends inside the IPOPT container path. Best for Shared lineage for MA57, MA77, MA86, MA87, and MA97 overlays. Avoid Using the family lineage without respecting per-backend acquisition and packaging constraints. Runtime eng-ipopt-onemkl/docker_image at birtha/knowledge-eng-ipopt-onemkl:1.0.0; environment ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_ipopt_onemkl_docker; healthcheck commands python scripts/verify_knowledge_runtime.py --environment-ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_ipopt_onemkl_docker; verification refs artifact://verification-report/7c82cce3-ffdc-5f4e-bb13-a70a51369bf2. GUI state PLANNED_CONTAINER_GUI; default GUI session artifact://gui-session-spec/eng_ipopt_onemkl_gui; control provider noVNC via OpenClaw browser. Runtime gate: CoinHSL sources are staged locally, but the canonical IPOPT plus CoinHSL container has not been verified in this sprint..\nGeometry Native Family: solves Canonical family packaging for geometry-native kernels and geometry-adjacent runtime surfaces. Best for Shared lineage for CGAL, OpenCAMLib, and PicoGK/ShapeKernel overlays. Avoid Treating the family pack as a substitute for a named geometry kernel. Runtime eng-geometry-native-family/docker_image at birtha/knowledge-eng-geometry-native-family:1.0.0; environment ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_geometry_native_family_docker; healthcheck commands python scripts/verify_knowledge_runtime.py --environment-ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_geometry_native_family_docker; verification refs artifact://verification-report/21b7505b-83b9-5865-9c71-2c303aed105b. GUI state PLANNED_CONTAINER_GUI; default GUI session artifact://gui-session-spec/eng_geometry_native_family_gui; control provider noVNC via OpenClaw browser. Runtime gate: Geometry-native family manifests are linked, but the canonical family runtime has not been verified in this sprint..\nNLP Time Chemistry Family: solves Canonical family packaging for nonlinear optimization, time integration, and chemistry-side kernels. Best for Shared lineage for IPOPT, SUNDIALS, and TChem child overlays. Avoid Treating the family pack as a replacement for a named solver runtime. Runtime eng-nlp-time-chem-family/docker_image at birtha/knowledge-eng-nlp-time-chem-family:1.0.0; environment ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_nlp_time_chem_family_docker; healthcheck commands python scripts/verify_knowledge_runtime.py --environment-ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_nlp_time_chem_family_docker; verification refs artifact://verification-report/fef209a2-4dab-51a2-b261-dc40c39d22be. GUI state PLANNED_CONTAINER_GUI; default GUI session artifact://gui-session-spec/eng_nlp_time_chem_family_gui; control provider noVNC via OpenClaw browser. Runtime gate: NLP, time-integration, and chemistry family manifests are linked, but the canonical family runtime has not been verified in this sprint..\nIntel oneMKL: solves Dense and sparse numerical kernels reused across containerized optimization backends, Canonical BLAS/LAPACK and sparse backend surface for the Phase 2 nonlinear stack. Best for Canonical substitute runtime for the prior PARDISO lane, Shared numeric backend support inside the IPOPT plus CoinHSL container path. Avoid Treating oneMKL as a standalone engineering solver without a host algorithm. Runtime eng-ipopt-onemkl/docker_image at birtha/knowledge-eng-ipopt-onemkl:1.0.0; environment ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_ipopt_onemkl_docker; healthcheck commands python scripts/verify_knowledge_runtime.py --environment-ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_ipopt_onemkl_docker; verification refs artifact://verification-report/82b7a37e-2324-56ad-a62e-ef2d3ae8414a. GUI state PLANNED_CONTAINER_GUI; default GUI session artifact://gui-session-spec/eng_ipopt_onemkl_gui; control provider noVNC via OpenClaw browser. Aliases: PARDISO. Substitution: Canonical pack used in place of the previously planned PARDISO acquisition path..\nPETSc Family: solves Canonical family packaging for PETSc-centered linear, nonlinear, and eigensolver backends. Best for Shared backend lineage for PETSc child overlays and wrappers. Avoid Treating the family pack as a substitute for a concrete PETSc child module. Runtime eng-petsc-family/docker_image at birtha/knowledge-eng-petsc-family:1.0.0; environment ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_petsc_family_docker; healthcheck commands python scripts/verify_knowledge_runtime.py --environment-ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_petsc_family_docker; verification refs artifact://verification-report/1b81c83f-b4e0-5068-908e-a26fc7e17cb8. GUI state PLANNED_CONTAINER_GUI; default GUI session artifact://gui-session-spec/eng_petsc_family_gui; control provider noVNC via OpenClaw browser. Runtime gate: PETSc family manifests are linked, but the canonical backend-family runtime has not been verified in this sprint..\nSparse Direct Family: solves Canonical family packaging for sparse-direct factorization and linear solve backends. Best for Shared lineage for MUMPS, SuperLU, SuiteSparse, and related child overlays. Avoid Treating the family pack as a drop-in replacement for a named sparse-direct backend. Runtime eng-sparse-direct-family/docker_image at birtha/knowledge-eng-sparse-direct-family:1.0.0; environment ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_sparse_direct_family_docker; healthcheck commands python scripts/verify_knowledge_runtime.py --environment-ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_sparse_direct_family_docker; verification refs artifact://verification-report/8170a12e-53c8-5f2b-bc9c-3b2cf19c907d. GUI state PLANNED_CONTAINER_GUI; default GUI session artifact://gui-session-spec/eng_sparse_direct_family_gui; control provider noVNC via OpenClaw browser. Runtime gate: Sparse-direct family manifests are linked, but the canonical backend-family runtime has not been verified in this sprint..\nTrilinos Family: solves Canonical family packaging for Trilinos solver, preconditioner, and multigrid overlays. Best for Shared backend lineage for Trilinos child overlays. Avoid Treating the family pack as a substitute for a concrete Trilinos package. Runtime eng-trilinos-family/docker_image at birtha/knowledge-eng-trilinos-family:1.0.0; environment ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_trilinos_family_docker; healthcheck commands python scripts/verify_knowledge_runtime.py --environment-ref artifact://environment-spec/eng_trilinos_family_docker; verification refs artifact://verification-report/6222437b-ba93-50c1-bd50-f5fb3223b0c2. GUI state PLANNED_CONTAINER_GUI; default GUI session artifact://gui-session-spec/eng_trilinos_family_gui; control provider noVNC via OpenClaw browser. Runtime gate: Trilinos family manifests are linked, but the canonical backend-family runtime has not been verified in this sprint..",
